Base Url:http://localhost:5000


Auth
1.POST /api/auth/register → create user.

2.POST /api/auth/login → login (super-admin via env or normal user).
Request body:
email: admin@example.com
password: admin@123

3.GET /api/secure/users → list users (super-admin only).

Providers (auth required; owner-scoped)

4.POST /api/providers → create provider.

5.GET /api/providers → list own providers (filters: status, name).

6.GET /api/providers/:id → get provider by id (owned).

7.PATCH /api/providers/:id → update provider (owned).

8.DELETE /api/providers/:id → delete provider (owned).


Add Bearer Token for all apis to work for providers